<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很快，<delay8 />这座<tag a="110" b="32" />的
首次大型活动就要开始了。<delay20 />
大家都在热议这件事，<delay8 />你听说了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻，<delay20 />真是令人期待啊！<delay frames="40" />
让我们一起来炒热气氛，<delay8 />
把活动办好吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就在明天，<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="33" />的第一个大型活动<delay8 />
终于要举办啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可得鼓起干劲，<delay8 />
要让这个活动热闹起来才行～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个周六有钓鱼大赛哦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你当然也会参加的，<delay20 />对不对？<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />钓鱼不用跑来跑去，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也不会累得满头大汗，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />简直是最适合我了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是钓鱼大赛了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经准备齐全了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呀，<delay20 />昨天就已经搜罗了
所有需要的道具。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />话虽如此，<delay20 />
其实也就只有一根钓竿而已啦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这周六是捕虫大赛呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />老实说，<delay8 />我其实
不太擅长捕虫，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我一定会竭尽全力的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是捕虫大赛了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也按照自己的步调<delay8 />
尽量努力吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经<delay8 />做好准备了吗？<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天早上，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快乐家协会就会对我们的家做出评价了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />收拾房间，或者装点一下<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可要抓紧<delay8 />
这最后的机会了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
从快乐家协会发回来的评价，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经看过了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得这份居住评价简直就像一面镜子。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然自己心里也清楚，<delay8 />
一定要认真接受它<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来今年应该也能安然度过了……<10_4 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的，<delay8 />这一年过得实在太快啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过换个角度想，这也证明我过得很开心吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay20 />今年也该有始有终才行。<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最后一天就去广场上，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和大家一起倒计时吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">明天，<tag a="90" b="27" />年就结束了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总感觉有些不踏实<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然如此，那就在倒计时的祭典上<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />彻底给今年画上句点，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再用放空的心态去迎接新年吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>